name: IMDB Top Rated Movies Dataset
description:
This dataset consists of all top-rated movies featured on the IMDB website. The dataset is fetched from TMDB API. Unnecessary columns are removed. There are 9335 movie entries with no null values.

Hope you enjoy working with this.

Contact me at smaindola90@gmail.com for more info.

distribution__description: The file contains 9335 rows and 9 columns. There are no null values.
recordSet__field__description: Name of the movie in english language
Date on which the movie was released
Genres of the movie. The values are comma separated.
keywords: subject > arts and entertainment > movies and tv shows

recordSet__field__description: Language which the movie was shot in originally
Number of votes/ratings for the movie
